"title": "5838: disrespect",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5838: disrespect",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The attitude of heart that leads people to treat God and others in ways that demonstrate a lack of esteem.</p>\n<h2>Causes of disrespect for God and Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Disrespect caused by a wrong view of God and Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:21–1:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:8-Luke23:11\">LUK 23:8–23:11</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect caused by disobedience to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:26\">NEH 9:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:17-2Chr24:20\">2CH 24:17–24:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:5\">2TI 3:1–3:5</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect caused by Satan</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3\">ACT 5:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:28-Matt8:29\">MAT 8:28–8:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:1-Mark5:7\">MRK 5:1–5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:26-Luke8:28\">LUK 8:26–8:28</a></p>\n<h2>Causes of disrespect for others</h2>\n<h3>Disrespect for others caused by a wrong view of people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:13-Matt19:14\">MAT 19:13–19:14</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:13-Mark10:14\">MRK 10:13–10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:15-Luke18:16\">LUK 18:15–18:16</a> <em>The lack of respect for the children arose from the erroneous belief that they were not important enough for Jesus Christ to bother with.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:25-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:25–10:37</a> <em>Those who passed by failed to heed God's command to love their neighbours as themselves</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:1-Jas2:4\">JAS 2:1–2:4</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect for others caused by seeking power and wealth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:1\">ECC 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:6\">JAS 5:1–5:6</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect for others caused by envy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:1-Mic2:2\">MIC 2:1–2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:3-Gen37:4\">GEN 37:3–37:4</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect for others caused by pride and contempt</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:18\">PSA 31:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:27-Matt27:31\">MAT 27:27–27:31</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:16-Mark15:20\">MRK 15:16–15:20</a></p>\n<h2>Disrespect shown in speech</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:9\">JAS 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:39-Matt27:44\">MAT 27:39–27:44</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:29-Mark15:32\">MRK 15:29–15:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:35-Luke23:39\">LUK 23:35–23:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:3-1Tim6:5\">1TI 6:3–6:5</a></p>\n<h2>The development of disrespect</h2>\n<h3>Disrespect can grow insidiously</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs11:4\">1KI 11:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:1-Jer2:11\">JER 2:1–2:11</a>MRK <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:15-Jer11:17\">11:15–11:17</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:12-Matt21:13\">MAT 21:12–21:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:45-Luke19:46\">LUK 19:45–19:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:13-John2:17\">JHN 2:13–2:17</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect can spread infectiously</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:27-Deut1:28\">DEU 1:27–1:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth1:16-Esth1:18\">EST 1:16–1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:9-Mark15:15\">MRK 15:9–15:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:17-Matt27:26\">MAT 27:17–27:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:13-Luke23:25\">LUK 23:13–23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:24\">ROM 2:24</a></p>\n<h3>Disrespect can end fatally</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev10:1-Lev10:2\">LEV 10:1–10:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:25-Exod32:28\">EXO 32:25–32:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:21\">DEU 21:18–21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:4-Jer25:11\">JER 25:4–25:11</a></p>",
